Package: gnome-shell-extension-fadeout
Version: 0.1.0
Section: gnome
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 47~)
Maintainer: laan <laan@laan.dev>
Homepage: https://github.com/laan/fadeout
Description: Dim unfocused windows in GNOME Shell
 FadeOut dims all windows except the currently focused one,
 helping you concentrate on the task at hand. Includes a
 panel indicator with a fade factor slider and a full
 preferences window.
